item.title: Overcoming toxic positivity with Susan David
item.description: Adam and psychologist Susan David examines the skills involved in emotional agility, discussing the risks of judging and suppressing unwanted emotions — and effective techniques for managing them. Feed: https://feeds.feedburner.com/WorklifeWithAdamGrant
